---
import { EXAM_MODES } from '../data/modes';

const year = new Date().getFullYear();
const AUTHOR = 'Alejandro Olivera';
const GITHUB = 'https://github.com/AlejandroOlivera';
---

<footer class="site-footer">
  <div class="road-line" role="presentation"></div>
  <div class="container inner">
    <div class="cols">
      <!-- Marca -->
      <div class="col col--brand">
        <span class="fbrand">
          <span class="fbrand__sign" aria-hidden="true">
            <span class="dot dot--red"></span>
            <span class="dot dot--amber"></span>
            <span class="dot dot--green"></span>
          </span>
          <strong>Taller B1</strong>
        </span>
        <p class="tagline">
          Practica para el examen teorico de conduccion (Licencia B1) en Colombia,
          con la estructura del CALE y la normativa vigente.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Practica -->
      <nav class="col" aria-label="Temas de practica">
        <h2 class="col__title">Practica</h2>
        <ul class="links">
          {
            EXAM_MODES.map((mode) => (
              <li>
                <a href={`/examen/${mode.slug}`}>{mode.short}</a>
              </li>
            ))
          }
        </ul>
      </nav>

      <!-- Fuentes / legal -->
      <div class="col">
        <h2 class="col__title">Normativa</h2>
        <p class="legal">
          Basado en la Ley 769 de 2002 y reformas (1383/2010, 1696/2013, 2161/2021,
          2251/2022) y la Resolucion 20253040037125 de 2025 (CALE).
        </p>
        <p class="legal">
          Material de estudio. No esta afiliado a ninguna entidad oficial ni reemplaza
          el examen del CALE. Verifica la normativa en
          <a href="https://www.mintransporte.gov.co">mintransporte.gov.co</a>.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="bottom">
      <p class="copy">
        © {year} · Proyecto de
        <a href={GITHUB} rel="author noopener" target="_blank">{AUTHOR}</a>
      </p>
      <p class="made">
        <a class="gh" href={GITHUB} rel="noopener" target="_blank">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 16 16" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true" fill="currentColor">
            <path d="M8 0C3.58 0 0 3.58 0 8a8 8 0 0 0 5.47 7.59c.4.07.55-.17.55-.38 0-.19-.01-.82-.01-1.49-2.01.37-2.53-.5-2.69-.95-.09-.23-.48-.95-.82-1.14-.28-.15-.68-.52-.01-.53.63-.01 1.08.58 1.23.82.72 1.21 1.87.87 2.33.66.07-.52.28-.87.51-1.07-1.78-.2-3.64-.89-3.64-3.95 0-.87.31-1.59.82-2.15-.08-.2-.36-1.02.08-2.12 0 0 .67-.21 2.2.82a7.4 7.4 0 0 1 2-.27c.68 0 1.36.09 2 .27 1.53-1.04 2.2-.82 2.2-.82.44 1.1.16 1.92.08 2.12.51.56.82 1.27.82 2.15 0 3.07-1.87 3.75-3.65 3.95.29.25.54.73.54 1.48 0 1.07-.01 1.93-.01 2.2 0 .21.15.46.55.38A8 8 0 0 0 16 8c0-4.42-3.58-8-8-8Z"></path>
          </svg>
          GitHub
        </a>
        <span>· Hecho para practicar, no reemplaza el examen oficial.</span>
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>

<style>
  .site-footer {
    margin-top: 4rem;
    background: var(--asphalt);
    color: #c2c8cf;
  }
  .inner {
    padding-block: 2.25rem 2.5rem;
  }

  .cols {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1.4fr 1fr 1.6fr;
    gap: 2rem;
  }
  @media (max-width: 760px) {
    .cols {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 1.6rem;
    }
  }

  .col__title {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    color: #fff;
    margin: 0 0 0.7rem;
  }

  .fbrand {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.6rem;
  }
  .fbrand__sign {
    display: inline-flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 3px;
    padding: 5px;
    background: #11151a;
    border-radius: 8px;
  }
  .dot {
    width: 9px;
    height: 9px;
    border-radius: 50%;
  }
  .dot--red {
    background: var(--signal-red);
  }
  .dot--amber {
    background: var(--signal-amber);
  }
  .dot--green {
    background: var(--signal-green);
  }
  .fbrand strong {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    color: #fff;
  }
  .tagline {
    margin: 0.8rem 0 0;
    font-size: 0.88rem;
    max-width: 38ch;
    color: #aab0b8;
  }

  .links {
    list-style: none;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 0.4rem 1rem;
  }
  .links a {
    color: #c2c8cf;
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 0.92rem;
  }
  .links a:hover {
    color: #fff;
  }

  .legal {
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    line-height: 1.5;
    color: #9aa1a9;
    margin: 0 0 0.6rem;
  }
  .legal a {
    color: #f0c668;
  }

  .bottom {
    margin-top: 1.8rem;
    padding-top: 1.2rem;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 0.6rem 1.2rem;
  }
  .copy {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 0.86rem;
    color: #c2c8cf;
  }
  .copy a {
    color: #fff;
    font-weight: 600;
  }
  .made {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: #8a9099;
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .gh {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.35rem;
    color: #c2c8cf;
    font-weight: 600;
  }
  .gh:hover {
    color: #fff;
    text-decoration: none;
  }
</style>
